{"tid":1718705,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"古代學術研究 - 投石索","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T02:35:12.000Z","uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b106e23f3a47c31d57900d0d8a2670003b5cea15","tid":1718705,"uid":130203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:07:47.000Z","msg":"-聖經中大衛就用投石索擊殺了巨人歌利亞<br />\n<br />\n-普通投石的穿透性自然不如弓箭，但是在面對着鐵甲目標時，<br />\n鈍擊傷害的石塊往往表現的比弓弩更好。投石索與弓弩相比彈藥便宜，<br />\n發射速度快，對士兵力量要求不高，對體力消耗也小，又可同時裝備盾牌。<br />\n但同時投石索也有缺陷，準確性低，個人需要空間大，無法集中部署，而且訓練難度大。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 人多地方唔好試, 對古代遊戲有興趣可以整完去郊外試玩下<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/news/5e4jj6.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fnews%2F5e4jj6.html&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZIyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=66855bfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/news/5e4jj6.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://life.tw/?app=view&amp;no=394253\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flife.tw%2F%3Fapp%3Dview%26no%3D394253&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZIyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=48c032b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://life.tw/?app=view&amp;no=394253</a>"},{"pid":"79ad6cc0b79375961f3c80e078ac67b8da4402b5","tid":1718705,"uid":21646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"咩都唔識好易tk"},{"pid":"f223a03883a3357c998ac46fc3aeab6aeaa12b8b","tid":1718705,"uid":332610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:29:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老味耐唔耐就有人POST出黎<br />\n朝朝都有"},{"pid":"99d9ef083ec9a2cdf599275cb5b380dae86b2198","tid":1718705,"uid":132729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:35:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老味連聖經入面點點點都拎黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老味不如叫手足用魔杖去攻擊啦?哈利波特入面都有教你唸個咒就殺到人,你唔係唔學呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}